地区的限制，所以才会无法使用。客服称，iPhone 也可以实现地震预警功能：第一步，开启「振动」开关；第二步，需要搭配一个第三方地震预警 App，可以在应用商店下载。苹果客服回应 iPhone 不支持地震预警：下载第三方 App 可实现 注：本问题前提有误，题主给出的例子中的软件为第三方软件，具体可点击为什么 apple 没有在系统层面接入国家地震预警系统，而只是推出了地震预警 App？ 这一次宜宾地震，华为，小米，OPPO，vivo，魅族等国产安卓厂商都有地震预警，而推出了车祸检测的苹果，为何没有在系统层面推出地震预警功能而只是推出了一个「地震预警」 App。 要知道 App 和系统内置在响应速度，以及可靠性上，便捷性上都不是一个级别。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/30a8e4775.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "165 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/599043086"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IxoyE/M+9ydBIEAMaCDk1NDAxMzcwIKSEzqIGMAA4XEAJcgk1OTkwNDMwODZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1691384609.756380", "card_id": "Q_615913254", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 65}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《海贼王》动画第 1071 集（五档路飞动画登场）？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-e8067e281d41332fd163acccde63e78c_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "157 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/615913254"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IxoyE/M+9ydBIEAMaCDk5MTQ5NjY3IKaXvKYGMAA4TEAKcgk2MTU5MTMyNTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1691384609.760196", "card_id": "Q_615938782", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 907}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "TFBOYS 十周年演唱会怎么样？看过后符合你的期待吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如题 特别想知道，花天价买了内场票的粉丝觉得值得吗？以及，被震撼到的西安人觉得欢迎吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-50d18d0b58